= Changqing Fu 

~~~
{}{img_left}{pic/pic.jpg}{Profile Pic}{160}{200}{}

*Research Interests*: Computer Vision and Machine Learning

Welcome! I'm a senior-year PhD student in CEREMADE, Université de Paris IX - Dauphine - PSL, and PR\[AI\]RIE Institute, fortunately advised by [https://www.ceremade.dauphine.fr/~cohen/ Laurent Cohen]. Before that I recieved a Bachelor's degree from School of Mathematical Sciences in Fudan University advised by [https://mastone1983.github.io/ Lei Shi], and a Master's degree in Theoretical and Applied Mathematics from Paris IX - PSL advised by [https://www.ceremade.dauphine.fr/~mula/ Olga Mula] and [https://sites.google.com/site/robryd/ Robin Ryder]. I was then a graduate student in University at Albany, State University of New York advised by [https://www.albany.edu/~yy298919/ Yiming Ying]. 

Here are my [https://prairie-institute.fr/chairs/fu-changqing/ Institutional Page], [pdf/CV.pdf CV], [https://www.facebook.com/davidfcq Facebook], [https://github.com/EvergreenTree GitHub], [http://www.linkedin.com/in/cqfu-fdu Linkedin] and some [pictures.html pictures of mine]:)

